CSA Pilots May Start Protest Over Layoffs Next Week, CTK Says

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-07-27T15:25:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/csa-pilots-may-start-protest-over-layoffs-next-week-ctk-says.html
Ceske Aerolinie AS, or CSA, pilots
may start a planned strike on Aug. 1 against further staff lay-
offs by the company,  CTK  reported, citing the Czech Association
of Passenger Jet Pilots head Filip Gaspar.  The protests against notices that CSA started to hand to
pilots today may result in flight delays or cancellations, the
newswire said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lenka Ponikelska in Prague 
 lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  